</b></p>
<p><b>expression and of the media, in compliance with international standards (Italy); 
</b></p>
<p>148.37. <b>Continue developing the institutional framework with respect to the 
</b></p>
<p><b>promotion and protection of human rights (Jordan); 
</b></p>
<p>148.38. <b>Continue its efforts to strengthen the framework for the protection 
</b></p>
<p><b>and promotion of human rights (Kazakhstan); 
</b></p>
<p>148.39. <b>Continue to work to fully secure the rights of the child (Russian 
</b></p>
<p><b>Federation); 
</b></p>
<p>148.40. <b>Continue its policies in improving women</b>&#8217;s<b> rights (Jordan); 
</b></p>
