</b></p>
<p>148.79. Additional steps be put in place to protect women&#8217;s rights more 
</p>
<p><b>effectively in rural areas in particular (Japan); 
</b></p>
<p>148.80. <b>Carry on the efforts for the empowerment of women and provide 
</b></p>
<p><b>employment opportunities for women (Oman); 
</b></p>
<p>148.81. <b>Carry on intensifying programs and activities aiming at raising 
</b></p>
<p><b>human rights awareness (Oman); 
</b></p>
