</b></p>
<p>149.23. <b>All areas of the judiciary be completely independent from the 
</b></p>
<p><b>executive (Denmark); 
</b></p>
<p>149.24. <b>Protect the judiciary against all interference from bodies belonging to 
</b></p>
<p><b>other branches of government (Switzerland); 
