<p><b>judiciary (Namibia); 
</b></p>
<p>149.26. <b>Ensure the independence and impartiality of the judiciary 
</b></p>
<p><b>(Uruguay); 
</b></p>
<p>149.27. <b>Conduct effective investigation on the case of murder of Hrant Dink, 
</b></p>
