<p><b>that freedom of expression is safeguarded in all forms, including the arts 
</b></p>
<p><b>(Norway); 
</b></p>
<p>149.35. <b>Respect the right to freedom of assembly as well as to carry out 
</b></p>
<p><b>investigations into excessive use of force by security forces against peaceful 
</b></p>
<p><b>protesters (Austria); 
</b></p>
<p>149.36. <b>Guarantee freedom of assembly and association, including by 
</b></p>
